      <h1 class='title'>Ministry of Defence Police</h1>
    </div>
    <div class='commons-written-statements-sitting' id='content'>
      
      <cite class='section'>HC Deb 18 November 2003 vol 413 c30WS</cite>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_30ws' title='Col. 30WS &mdash; HC Deb 18 November 2003 vol 413 c30WS' name='column_30ws' href='#column_30ws' rel='bookmark'>30WS</a>
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0413P2_20031118_CWS_5'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-geoff-hoon' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0413P2_20031118_CWS_5' title='Link to this speech by Mr Geoff Hoon' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-geoff-hoon" title="Mr Geoff Hoon">The Secretary of State for Defence (Mr. Geoffrey Hoon)</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para">In light of the recommendations made by the House of Commons Defence Committee as a result of the introduction of the <a href="/acts/anti-terrorism-crime-and-security-act-2001">Anti-Terrorism, Crime and Security Act 2001</a>, I am pleased to place in the Library of the House on behalf of the Ministry of Defence Police their Operational Report for the year 2002&#x2013;03.</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
